listing.name: Two Level Amsterdam Apartment
listing.description: located in a quiet part of Amsterdam, walking distance to major tourist attractions, stone throw away from De Waag (Nieuwmarkt Square).
listing.house_rules: We kindly request our guest to respect the house and our neighbours. No loud music is allowed after 10pm. Smoking and illegal drugs are prohibited in the house.
